        Product details
       <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-1 rounded-full text-blue" data-v-74832f47><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" role="img" focusable="false" data-component="ChevronIcon" class="ease-in-out duration-150 shrink-0 ease-in-out w-5 h-5 md:w-7 md:h-7 duration-300" data-v-74832f47><rect x="9.87646" y="14.9978" width="11.5" height="3" rx="0.9" transform="rotate(-45 9.87646 14.9978)" fill="currentColor"></rect> <rect x="5.9873" y="6.86595" width="11.5" height="3" rx="0.9" transform="rotate(45 5.9873 6.86595)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></div></h3> <!----> <div data-component="transition" class="accordion-item__body" style="display:none;" data-v-74832f47 data-v-74832f47><div class="pt-4" data-v-74832f47><div class="text-blue" data-v-73148c55>Minotaur's ball pein hammer is the ideal tool for metalwork. The spherical 'pein' edge is great for shaping metal, setting rivets and driving chisels, while the flat edge can be used for countless different tasks in the worlds of construction, plumbing and household DIY.<br />On a more technical side, the head weight of this hammer is 16 oz (1lb) so it's hefty enough to take on whatever you throw at it. It's also been made from a hardened and tempered drop-forged steel alloy, which means it's very strong and wear-resistant. The fibreglass shaft is both lightweight and robust.<br />You'll find the TPR ergonomically designed soft-grip handle is comfortable to hold - this means less chance of tired wrists if used for extended periods of time. Durability is covered too, as the head has been fully polished for extra corrosion resistance.<br />• Hardened and tempered drop-forged alloy steel is strong and durable<br />• Fully polished head on a fibreglass shaft<br />• TPR soft-grip handle remains comfortable to hold during longer jobs<br />• 16oz head weight suitable for a variety of jobs</div></div></div></div> <div id="reviews" class="accordion-item" data-v-74832f47 data-v-73148c55><h3 class="accordion-item__title" data-v-74832f47><div class="flex items-center gap-8" data-v-74832f47 data-v-73148c55><span data-v-74832f47 data-v-73148c55>Reviews</span> <span aria-hidden="true" class="stars text-size-6.5" data-v-0b46bfce data-v-73148c55>
